---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="研究成果 - WZULTC" description="文藻跨語照護計畫研究成果與出版品">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-5xl">
    <!-- Page Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">
        研究成果
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
        學術研究與實務應用
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Introduction -->
    <section class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">
        研究方向
      </h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>
          本計畫結合華語教學、跨文化溝通與長照實務，
          進行多面向的研究探討。
        </p>
        <p>
          研究成果不僅發表於學術期刊，更實際應用於教材開發與教學實務，
          為移工華語教育領域提供重要參考。
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Research Areas -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-50 to-rose-50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3 flex items-center">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-2 text-pink-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
          </svg>
          華語教學研究
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">針對越南移工的華語學習需求與教學策略研究</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-cyan-50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3 flex items-center">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-2 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
          跨文化溝通
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">台越文化差異與跨文化適應相關研究</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-emerald-50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3 flex items-center">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-2 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
          </svg>
          教材開發
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">照護華語教材設計與開發研究</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-indigo-50 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3 flex items-center">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-2 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
          </svg>
          成效評估
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">教學成效與學習者回饋分析研究</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Publications Coming Soon -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-50 to-purple-50 rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">
        出版品與論文
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        研究成果與出版品資訊即將更新，敬請期待。
      </p>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="inline-block bg-pink-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-pink-700 transition-colors"
      >
        索取相關資料
      </a>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
